transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Hey, thanks for calling Viagra, how can I help you?

Speaker 2: Yes, I just made a purchase through Discord Blue, and I'm just trying to find out, do—

Speaker 1: You have the tracking?

Speaker 2: Yeah, we definitely will.

Speaker 1: Did you just place the order now?

Speaker 2: What's your first and last name?

Speaker 1: First name, Wesley, W-E-S-T-L-E-Y.

Speaker 2: Last name, Green, E-R-E-E-N.

Speaker 1: And your address, Mr. Green?

Speaker 2: 2849 Sussex Close, Lithia Springs, Georgia 30122.

Speaker 1: Okay, perfect.

Speaker 2: So I see your order has been placed.

Speaker 1: It's still processing.

Speaker 2: It hasn't, I don't think, been approved yet.

Speaker 1: Yeah, it hasn't been approved yet, Mr. Green, but that'll happen within like the next couple—

Speaker 2: Hours or so.

Speaker 1: The order's not going to go out today because we're done shipping for the day.

Speaker 2: It's just a little bit late in the afternoon for us.

Speaker 1: But it will go out tomorrow, and then you will get a tracking number.

Speaker 2: Yeah, if you don't get that tracking number by like this time tomorrow, give us a call—

Speaker 1: Back, and we definitely will provide that for you over the phone.

Speaker 2: But you should get an email with that, too.

Speaker 1: Okay, that sounds like a plan.

Speaker 2: Yeah, it'll go out tomorrow, Friday, and then three to five business days, you'll see it—

Speaker 1: Arrive with USPS.

Speaker 2: That's your regular postman.

Speaker 1: Oh, okay, that's pretty quick, then.

Speaker 2: Will it be anonymous?

Speaker 1: Yeah, very similar to those Amazon bags that they send out.

Speaker 2: It looks very similar to that.

Speaker 1: It'll just have your name and address on it.

Speaker 2: Okay, thank you.

Speaker 1: And who am I talking to?

Speaker 2: My name is Leo.

Speaker 1: Thank you, Leo.

Speaker 2: No problem, Mr. Green.

Speaker 1: You've been very helpful.

Speaker 2: Of course, of course.

Speaker 1: If you need anything else, feel free to give us a shout anytime.

Speaker 2: Okay, and at any time, if I wanted to upgrade to the pill or to how many pills, I can always—

Speaker 1: Do that online, or I can call it in?

Speaker 2: Yeah, absolutely.

Speaker 1: If you ever need to make any changes and you have trouble online, give us a call, and we'll—

Speaker 2: Help you out over the phone.

Speaker 1: No problem.

Speaker 2: All right.

Speaker 1: All right, thank you, Leo.

Speaker 2: Enjoy the rest of your day.

Speaker 1: You as well.

Speaker 2: Thank you.

Speaker 1: Bye-bye now.
